[[中国|中国]]是世界風力發電的領先者，擁有世界上最大的裝機容量家，并且保持快速增长<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://www.worldwindconf.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/Wu-Gang.pdf|title = Wind Matters: China's Role in the Future of Wind|date =2015-10-28|access-date = 2016-02-08|website = |publisher = Goldwind|last = Gang|first = Wu|deadurl = yes|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20170104230732/http://www.worldwindconf.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/Wu-Gang.pdf|archivedate = 2017-01-04}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title = China's new wind power capacity hits record high |url = http://news.xinhuanet.com/english/2016-02/03/c_135069164.htm| publisher = Xinhua News |access-date = 2016-02-08|archive-date = 2016-02-03|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160203013013/http://news.xinhuanet.com/english/2016-02/03/c_135069164.htm|dead-url = yes}}</ref>。中國拥有广阔的疆域和漫长的海岸线，因此具有十分丰富的[[风能|风能]]资源<ref>[http://ewea.org/fileadmin/ewea_documents/documents/publications/reports/Offshore_Report_2009.pdf Oceans of Opportunity: Harnessing Europe's largest domestic energy resource] {{Wayback|url=http://ewea.org/fileadmin/ewea_documents/documents/publications/reports/Offshore_Report_2009.pdf |date=20191014124816 }} pp. 18-19.</ref>。据估计，中国陸地拥有2380 GW的可开发容量，同时海洋有200 GW的可开发容量<ref>[http://www.windpowermonthly.com/article/1107732/Wind-provides-15-Chinas-electricity Wind provides 1.5% of China's electricity] {{Wayback|url=http://www.windpowermonthly.com/article/1107732/Wind-provides-15-Chinas-electricity |date=20190514114912 }} Wind Power Monthly, 2011-12-05</ref>。截至2020年底，風電是中國第三大電力來源，佔總發電量的6.1%。<ref>{{Cite web|title=China: power generation by source 2020|url=https://www.statista.com/statistics/302233/china-power-generation-by-source/|access-date=2021-03-11|website=Statista|language=en|archive-date=2021-12-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211230025929/https://www.statista.com/statistics/302233/china-power-generation-by-source/}}</ref>根据{{le|全球风能理事会|Global Wind Energy Council}}《2022年全球风能报告》的统计，2021年中国陆上风电新增装机容量30.7 GW，占全球42.34%，海上风电新增装机容量占全球80.02%<ref>{{cite news|title=中国第一！全球各国风电装机Top10排名出炉|url=https://news.bjx.com.cn/html/20220406/1215342.shtml|accessdate=2022-04-07|publisher=北极星风力发电网|date=2022-04-06|archive-date=2022-04-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220406165601/https://news.bjx.com.cn/html/20220406/1215342.shtml}}</ref>。

2020年，中國新增風力發電71.6GW，總容量達到281GW。<ref>{{Cite news|last=Stanway|first=Muyu Xu, David|date=2021-01-21|title=China doubles new renewable capacity in 2020; still builds thermal plants|language=en|work=Reuters|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-china-energy-climatechange-idUSKBN29Q0JT|access-date=2021-03-11|archive-date=2022-05-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220511122735/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-china-energy-climatechange-idUSKBN29Q0JT}}</ref>。中国在2020年无论是装机容量还是新增容量均遙遙領先全球与第二大的市场[[美国|美国]]相比都有较大优势。美国在2020年中新增装机14GW，裝機容量為118GW。<ref>{{Cite web|title=The United States installed more wind turbine capacity in 2020 than in any other year - Today in Energy - U.S. Energy Information Administration (EIA)|url=https://www.eia.gov/todayinenergy/detail.php?id=46976|access-date=2021-03-11|website=www.eia.gov|archive-date=2022-05-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220516032400/https://www.eia.gov/todayinenergy/detail.php?id=46976}}</ref>到2030年，中國預計將擁有 1200 GW的風能和太陽能裝機容量。作為政府承諾的一部分，到該年將非化石燃料在一次能源消費中的份額提高到 25%左右。<ref>{{Cite news|author=Reuters Staff|date=2020-12-12|title=China aims to push wind and solar capacity beyond 1,200 GW by 2030|language=en|work=Reuters|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/climate-change-un-china-idUKL4N2IR2QX|access-date=2021-03-11|archive-date=2020-12-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201216125124/https://www.reuters.com/article/climate-change-un-china-idUKL4N2IR2QX}}</ref>在[[十二五规划|十二五规划]]中，中国已将风力发电确定为国家经济增长的一个关键组成。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/environment/2009/feb/03/wind-power-eu|title=Wind power becomes Europe's fastest growing energy source|publisher=Guardian|accessdate=2010-01-31|location=London|author=David Gow|date=2009-02-03|archive-date=2009-02-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090206090211/http://www.guardian.co.uk/environment/2009/feb/03/wind-power-eu|dead-url=no}}</ref>2020年底，中國政府制定了到2030年風能和太陽能總裝機容量達到1200GW的路線圖。<ref>{{Cite web|title=China Outlines Additional Steps on Climate Action|url=https://www.nrdc.org/experts/jake-schmidt/china-outlines-additional-steps-climate-action|access-date=2021-03-11|last=December 12|website=NRDC|language=en|last2=Chen|first2=2020 Jake Schmidt Alvin Lin Brendan Guy Han|archive-date=2022-04-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220418212746/https://www.nrdc.org/experts/jake-schmidt/china-outlines-additional-steps-climate-action}}</ref>

中國最大的國產風機製造商是[[金風科技|金風科技]]。 金風科技成立於1998年，積極開發新技術並擴大市場份額，但隨後從 2006 年的 35%下降到2012年的19%。<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Between fragmented authoritarianism and policy coordination: Creating a Chinese market for wind energy|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_energy-policy_2007-07_35_7/page/3879|first1=Adrian|last2=Ruby|first2=Kristian|journal=Energy Policy|issue=7|doi=10.1016/j.enpol.2007.01.025|year=2007|volume=35|pages=3879–3890|last1=Lema}}</ref>2019年，金風科技是首批簽約東北地區風電制氫項目的合作夥伴之一，希望充分利用中國目前尚未開發的風力發電潛力。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Goldwind joins 20GW hydrogen plan in China {{!}} REVE News of the wind sector in Spain and in the world|url=https://www.evwind.es/2019/07/20/goldwind-joins-20gw-hydrogen-plan-in-china/68122|access-date=2020-10-13|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-05-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210517103716/https://www.evwind.es/2019/07/20/goldwind-joins-20gw-hydrogen-plan-in-china/68122}}</ref>中國國電集團的另一家子公司中國龍源電力集團公司也是風電的早期先驅，曾一度運營著中國40%的風電場。<ref>{{cite web|title=Wind Energy Businesses in China|url=http://energy.sourceguides.com/businesses/byGeo/byC/China/byP/wRP/wRP.shtml|access-date=31 January 2010|website=Energy.sourceguides.com|archive-date=2018-08-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180815164310/http://energy.sourceguides.com/businesses/byGeo/byC/China/byP/wRP/wRP.shtml}}</ref>

根據Fitch Solutions的2020年預測，到2028年中國的風力發電量預計將達到約1000TWh，高於之前870TWh的預測，主因是科技的快速發展使項目成本降低變得可能。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Tech upgrades to push China's wind generation to 700TWh by 2028|url=https://asian-power.com/power-utility/news/tech-upgrades-push-chinas-wind-generation-700twh-2028|access-date=2020-10-13|website=Asian Power|archive-date=2022-01-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220128114307/https://asian-power.com/power-utility/news/tech-upgrades-push-chinas-wind-generation-700twh-2028}}</ref>

