2010年，中国成为全球最大的风力发电提供者，截至年底风力发电装机容量达41.8 MW，但其中约1/4未接入[[电网|电网]]<ref>{{cite web |author1=Matthew McDermott |title=One Quarter of China's Wind Power Still Not Connected to Electricity Grid |url=http://www.geni.org/globalenergy/library/technical-articles/generation/wind/treehugger/one-quarter-of-chinas-wind-power-still-not-connected-to-electricity-grid/index.shtml |publisher=Treehugger |accessdate=2022-04-07 |date=2011-03-12 |archive-date=2017-09-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170920000309/http://www.geni.org/globalenergy/library/technical-articles/generation/wind/treehugger/one-quarter-of-chinas-wind-power-still-not-connected-to-electricity-grid/index.shtml }}</ref>；2012年底，风力发电装机容量达到76 MW，但其中有15 MW未接入电网。根据全球风能理事会的观点，中国风能的发展在规模上和节奏上都绝对是世界上无与伦比的。[[全国人民代表大会常务委员会|全国人民代表大会常务委员会]]通过一项法律，要求中国能源公司购买所有可再生能源行业生产的电力<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.platts.com/RSSFeedDetailedNews/RSSFeed/ElectricPower/6773195 |title=Wind power installaton slowed in 2010, outlook for 2011 stronger: AWEA |accessdate=2014-12-20 |archive-date=2012-12-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121227114346/http://www.platts.com/RSSFeedDetailedNews/RSSFeed/ElectricPower/6773195 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

